        <p class="metadata">Posted by Ryan Mauger (bittarman) on 2010-06-16T09:58:00.000+0000</p> 
        <div class="body">
            <p>This is the expected behaviour.
Zend_Form::setAttribs() will empty all attribs before setting new ones.
Zend_Form::setAction() simply proxies to Zend_Form::setAttrib('action', $action)</p>

<p>This is because the action is an attribute, and therefore should be expected to be set with setAttrib|s also</p>

